text: The iconic DRUMSTICK experience is now available in a tub! Everything you love about DRUMSTICK Strawberry Cheesecake cones -- creamy strawberry cheesecake flavoured frozen dessert, a delicious strawberry ripple, and graham pieces-- are now all mixed together in a scoopable, shareable treat, perfect for enjoying with friends and family. Proudly crafted in Ontario, Canada, DRUMSTICK Strawberry Cheesecake is made with Canadian dairy and has no artificial colours. Create some joyful memories with DRUMSTICK Strawberry Cheesecake frozen dessert and try our other DRUMSTICK tub flavours -- Vanilla Caramel and Chocolate Fudge Brownie. DRUMSTICK, the original sundae cone experience since 1928.
